p-help-media-entertainment-translation-global-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-netflix-marvel-lucasfilm-holllywood-deepfake-dubbing-vc-funding-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooking%20to%20harness%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20media%20businesses%20scale.%20Dubbing%20in%20particular%20is%20a%20hot%20topic%20in%20the%20creator%20economy%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-tells-mark-zuckerberg-what-he-would-change-about-facebook-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20likes%20of%20MrBeast%3C%2Fa%3E%20championing%20the%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.youtube%2Fnews-and-events%2Fauto-dubbing-on-youtube%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20unveiled%20its%20own%20auto-dubbing%20features%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%2C%20which%20are%20currently%20available%20on%20a%20limited%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Tal%20contended%20that%20creating%20stand-alone%20channels%20results%20in%20better%20viewership.%20It%20allows%20for%20translated%20thumbnails%20and%20video%20descriptions%2C%20as%20well%20as%20comment%20sections%20that%20aren't%20clouded%20by%20different%20languages%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinguana's%20AI%20technology%20captures%20the%20tone%20of%20creators'%20voices%2C%20and%20the%20company%20works%20with%20human%20reviewers%20to%20verify%20its%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECMO%20Jonny%20Steel%20told%20BI%20that%20Linguana's%20goal%20was%20%26quot%3Bultimate%20authenticity%26quot%3B%20in%20making%20creators%20sound%20like%20they're%20speaking%20in%20the%20different%20languages%20themselves.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20had%20received%20feedback%20from%20creators%20that%20it%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigher%20quality%20of%20accuracy%26quot%3B%20than%20Google's%20auto-dubbing%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinguana%20doesn't%20charge%20up%20front.%20Rather%2C%