quot%3Bvictory.%26quot%3B%20Rack%20up%20enough%2C%20and%20it'll%20secure%20you%20a%20date%20with%20the%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20given%20about%20five%20minutes%20to%20flirt%20in%20each%20scenario.%20And%20I%20had%2010%20scenarios%20to%20play%20with%20in%20the%20free%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20game%20is%20powered%20by%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4o%20and%20GPT-4o%20mini%2C%20and%20Tinder%20says%20your%20awkward%20pickup%20lines%20won't%20be%20used%20to%20train%20any%20AI%20models.%20It's%20only%20available%20to%20iOS%20users%20in%20the%20US%20for%20a%20limited%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Tinder's%20parent%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatch-group-spencer-rascoff-employee-letter-online-app-critique-numbers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatch%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20the%20company%20is%20using%20the%20game%20%26quot%3Bto%20learn%20and%20explore%20what%20future%20rollouts%20in%20other%20markets%20might%20look%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20game%20comes%20as%20Match%20struggles%20with%20lower%20user%20numbers.%20The%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmatch-group-bumble-both-have-have-new-ceos-whitney-herd-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20bring%20the%20focus%20back%20to%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20project%20gave%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20experiment%20with%20how%20AI%20can%20make%20dating%20a%20little%20more%20fun%20and%20a%20little%20less%20intimidating%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alex%20Osborne%2C%20Match's%20senior%20director%20of%20product%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatch's%20stock%20is%20down%2010.8%25%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20while%20rival%20Bumble%20is%20down%2061%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22668375a7-cfb7-47c8-8fc2-4de647f1f09c%5C%22%3EI%20tried%20flirting%20(and%20failing)%20with%20Tinder's%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20scenario%20was%20labeled%20%26quot%3BEasy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20brought%20my%20usual%20self%20to%20the%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsabella%20started%20off%20strong%2C%20asking%20what%20brought%20me%20here.%20I%20complimented%20the%20lamp%20and%20said%20I%20liked%20crafts.%20I%20asked%20her%20what%20her%20favorite%20item%20in%20the%20store%20was%2C%20and%20she%20launched%20into%20a%20monologue%20about%20a%20handwoven%20carpet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20a%20visual%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20relate.%20And%20she%20sounded%20robotic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoping%20to%20steer%20flirtier%2C%20I%20asked%20what%20else%20she%20liked.%20She%20listed%20pottery%2C%20then%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20into%20it.%20I%20said%20yes%20%E2%80%94%20cue%20her%20AI-generated%20wisdom%20about%20the%20joy%20of%20surrounding%20yourself%20with%20things%20you%20make%20with%20your%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20my%20shot%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20like%20making%20with%20your%20hands%3F%26quot%3B%20(Cringe.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20answer%3A%20Custom%20lab%20notebooks%20and%20DIY%20molecular%20models.%20Hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feigned%20interest%2C%20the%20conversation%20fizzled%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20score%20a%20date.%20Tinder%20handed%20me%20some%20generic%20flirting%20tips%2C%20like%20%26quot%3Bask%20more%20about%20her%20favorite%20crafts.%26quot%3B%20Thanks%2C%20AI%20wingman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Isabella%20in%20the%20Tinder%20AI%20game.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ecf24c63d72727e198ec72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeet%20Isabella%2C%20a%20scientist%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20spark%20of%20curiosity.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ELee%20Chong%20Ming%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20a%20shot%20at%20romance%20with%20Jackson%2C%20a%20photographer%20at%20a%20lively%20block%20party.%20We%20were%20manning%20the%20grill%20together%20%E2%80%