er%20at%20this%20than%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20laughing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20realization%20has%20got%20him%20excited%20to%20harness%20the%20power%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20make%20some%20big%20decisions%20on%20where%20to%20concentrate%20the%20firepower%20and%20what%20workflows%20should%20be%20transformed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20advice%20to%20engineers%20working%20in%20or%20planning%20to%20work%20in%20Wall%20Street's%20tech%20ranks%20is%20to%20embrace%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20environment%20is%20constantly%20changing.%20This%20is%20especially%20true%20because%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20ripe%20for%20AI%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20much%20of%20the%20business%20is%20digitized%2C%20but%20the%20complexities%20of%20the%20business%20(from%20developing%20software%20for%20different%20financial%20instruments%20to%20the%20regulatory%20nuances%20of%20emerging%20markets)%20has%20largely%20held%20the%20industry%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20engineers%20interested%20in%20applying%20technology%20to%20solve%20interesting%20problems%2C%20and%20particularly%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20the%20AI%20disruption%20will%20occur%2C%20I%20think%20this%20actually%20would%20be%20an%20industry%20to%20watch%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaysinskiy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoint72-cto-ilya-gaysinskiy-tech-talent-ai-plans-hedge-fund-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743584822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ec0320b8b41a9673fc45d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpoint72-cto-ilya-gaysinskiy-tech-talent-ai-plans-hedge-fund-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20first%20interview%2C%20Ilya%20Gaysinskiy%20outlines%20his%20tech%20ambitions%20for%20Point72%2C%20from%20AI%20to%20global%20expansion%20and%20culture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bschan%40businessinsider.com%20(Bianca%20Chan